{"tid":482450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【直播李飛演講】李華明：有意義非洗腦　批政客誇張無限擴大","createTime":"2017-11-28T07:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T08:48:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a3cb122e39b027e2c8597ee20d51c59253c86170","tid":482450,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171128/s00001/0da2cf92c5434a14d6be58fe7632a286.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171128%2Fs00001%2F0da2cf92c5434a14d6be58fe7632a286.jpg&h=8af99723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會主任李飛早前來港就《基本法》演講，教育局鼓勵學校直播，被批評是「洗腦」。不過民主黨李華明指活動有意義，又說一次演講不能做到「洗腦」效果，認為「香港有些政客動不動就會以誇張及無限擴大的說法，指凡是中央官員或特區政府的說話便有洗腦效應」。<br />\n<br />\n李華明上周五於《am730》專欄撰寫題為＜催眠的基本法講座＞文章，提到李飛來港演講及教育局要求學校直播，被指摘為「洗腦」。<br />\n<br />\n他說，翻查維基資料，「洗腦」是「透過系統性方法，有意圖地向別人灌輸思想，來符合操縱者的意願，一連串的手法與過程」，惟安排中學生在禮堂聽李飛演講，「肯定不是洗腦！反而我會稱之為最佳的催眠」。<br />\n<br />\n李華明續指，「一次過的演講絕對不能做到洗腦的效果」，只是香港有些政客動不動以「誇張」及「無限擴大」說法，凡是中央官員或特區政府的說話便說有「洗腦」效應，但他表示，「對中學生最具影響力的，便是通識科的老師，網上的資訊及朋輩間的互相影響」。<br />\n<br />\n李華明指，今次是香港回歸20周年活動，「意義是肯定有的」，惟不應該直播，而是事後剪輯，讓老師和同學邊看邊討論，才能把《基本法》深入校園。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171128/s00001/1511851112670\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171128%2Fs00001%2F1511851112670&d=tcLTG%2BufxrLO4M7QpfdgM26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=381c09e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171128%2Fs00001%2F1511851112670&h=1a1ab3f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171128/s00001/1511851112670</a>"},{"pid":"a057a1f604376b47fe98f0a0525793c3fa1e1fac","tid":482450,"uid":30510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"民主黨"},{"pid":"73725a057cbc13659d7796a4301c50c0fa57f2f5","tid":482450,"uid":9348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:20:45.000Z","msg":"條撚樣幾時仆街死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0484009aa99225c317d347dd324d4f5efc6fc8","tid":482450,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民主黨</blockquote><br />\n賣香港賣到盡"},{"pid":"a7996f649ce8b3ef817888cc0de8568febfb1732","tid":482450,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:21:59.000Z","msg":"有咩意義？"},{"pid":"9db4cc41ed256ce0529ac94c93571c8bf49764e4","tid":482450,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:23:56.000Z","msg":"奶共狗有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091754bdb2d03fb8f771d795a83d89dd7b3b9ffb","tid":482450,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"賣香港"},{"pid":"5ec1174b5a1fad1a56bb473168a26e433d391a4c","tid":482450,"uid":128763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:29:03.000Z","msg":"共已投"},{"pid":"aa9c7c46296ae1f0829c6427d128c2419d9f37e5","tid":482450,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"有咩意義 ?"},{"pid":"3125fe184af9586c88faa81e84000c741737325f","tid":482450,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"屎忽鬼又幫共匪洗屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d524ab060b088f8bd4336c0b34b05d33d808e949","tid":482450,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>奶共咪認囉</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d0ace3e5d731ed179a1e6dcfc0296f687901d022","tid":482450,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T